message:
Replaces system-dependent line separator by %n in printf

Signed-off-by: Manoel Campos <manoelcampos@gmail.com>

added: System.out.printf("%nHosts CPU utilization history for the entire simulation period%n");
System.out.printf("Host %d: Number of PEs %2d, MIPS by PE %.0f%n", host.getId(), host.getNumberOfPes(), mipsByPe);
deleted: System.out.println("\nHosts CPU utilization history for the entire simulation period");
System.out.printf("Host %d: Number of PEs %2d, MIPS by PE %.0f\n", host.getId(), host.getNumberOfPes(), mipsByPe);
